description:
&lt;p&gt;A vacancy has arisen for a Clinical Support Worker, Band 3 within the medical division at Lister Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a CSW Band 3 who will assist the multi disciplinary team to provide expert clinical care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We invite applications from motivated, reliable CSWs with a proven track record, who are looking to take the next step in their career pathway.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We operate an 11.5 hour shift pattern.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should demonstrate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to personal and professional development. We are looking for enthusiastic candidates, dedicated to providing the highest level of nursing care. You must have good organisational and communication skills, be self motivated and a team player.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 2 years experience at Band 2, gained in an acute environment, and wish to work in a team where learning and development are actively encouraged.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rachel Bickerstaff&lt;/p&gt;
